After the block:

* print the outer `status`

## Go further

### A. Ignore the index with `_`

```go
for _, task := range tasks {
    fmt.Println(task)
}
```

### B. Use the index too

```go
for index, task := range tasks {
    fmt.Println(index, task)
}
```

### C. While-style loop

```go
countdown := 3
for countdown > 0 {
    fmt.Println(countdown)
    countdown--
}
```

